{"type":"message","id":"30e8092a","parentId":"626545cd","timestamp":"2026-03-26T16:29:09.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MCP only has `list_feeds`, `get_feed_detail`, `search_notes` is NOT available. It doesn't have a search function. The earlier search results came from a previous session that already had data.\n\nLet me try to use the MediaCrawler MCP or check if there's a way to get the小红书 post URL. Without a search function in the MCP, I can't directly search from here. The earlier search results were from before.\n\nActually, I think the earlier search results might have been from the bootstrap conversation context (which mentioned the results). But those were already provided to me in the conversation - so those were from the previous session where someone searched 小红书.\n\nNow the user wants the actual URL. Since I can't search without the search_notes tool, and the MCP doesn't have it, I need to either:\n\n\n1. Use browser to access xiaohongshu (but it needs login)\n2. Try to guess the URL format\n3. Tell the user I can't get the URL\n\nActually, looking back at the conversation, I see the search results from earlier - 4 items about 英雄联盟皮肤推荐 2026. The second most popular was \"这类皮肤千万别买\" with 1250 likes. But I don't have the actual URLs from those results, and the list_feeds tool only returns following/首页内容, not search results.\n\nThe MediaCrawler MCP at port 18080 isn't running, so I can't use that either. I should be honest with the user that I can't get the direct URL without the search tool available."},{"type":"text","text":"小红书 MCP 当前可用工具里**没有搜索功能**，只有`list_feeds`（首页流）和`get_feed_detail`（帖子详情）。\n\n之前搜到的结果是旧数据残留，没法拿到真实URL。\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. 你在手机上打开小红书 → 搜索「英雄联盟皮肤top100」→ 把帖子链接发给我\n2. 或者告诉我帖子标题，我帮你用其他方式找\n\n你现在方便发链接吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"